left_text: Submarginal cells two; propodeal triangle laterally about half length of metanotum (laterally)
right_text: Submarginal cells three; propodeal triangle laterally slightly more than half length of metanotum (laterally) or almost same length

left_text: Hind tibial spurs with apices curved like claws, subequal in length; vertex concave or almost straight in frontal view
right_text: Hind tibial spurs with apices only slightly curved, inner somewhat longer than outer; vertex convex in frontal view

left_text: Lateral ocellus, in frontal view, above upper orbital tangent; inner orbits divergent dorsally
right_text: Lateral ocellus, in frontal view, at same level as or slightly below upper orbital tangent; inner orbits convergent dorsally or almost subparallel

left_text: Outer subantennal suture almost straight; clypeus, inferior paraocular area, and base of mandible without yellow
right_text: Outer subantennal suture distinctly arcuate laterally; at least clypeus with yellow

left_text: Frontal line almost imperceptible; lower paraocular area and tegula without yellow
right_text: Frontal line distinct, in a groove; lower paraocular area and tegula with yellow
